Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:06.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Gaki no Tsukai presents the 1st, \N"Wait until weep! Cuckoo Championship~!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm not enthusiastic about this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is just at one's own timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:21.18,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone will be put in various situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.18,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:25.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,in which you'd cry for real at your own timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:32.06,onscreen-black,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(296,810)\c&H0E0FF2&\fs60}(Today's aim)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:32.06,onscreen-black,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(930,880)\fs60}(A {\c&H37FFF8&\3c&H070600&}contest of dramas {\c&H070600&\3c&HFFFFFF&}that will make you cry)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:26.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes... for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:28.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking forward to this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:34.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tsukitei-san seems relatively enthusiastic though
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.98,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,709)}Yeah, I worked hard for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:40.06,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What I heard was that Tsukitei-san and Tanaka-san were all in for this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1044,493)}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:44.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tsukitei-san and Tanaka-san want to earn as actors as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:45.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:48.54,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Endo-san wants to do the same but his acting skill just isn't up to par.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:55.88,Endo,,0,0,0,,Lacking in capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:02.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rules are quite simple: the act will continue until tears have been shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:05.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not a time trial race, however timing is paramount.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:07.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Giving up is also possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:09.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:11.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Basically, there's no talking involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:14.54,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, it's all about emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:20.11,onscreen-black,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(190,800)\fs60\c&H37FFF8&\3c&H070600&}(Rule 4)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:20.11,onscreen-black,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(824,869)\fs60}(Plays must be {\c&H11147D&}silent {\c&H070600&\3c&HFFFFFF&}with no lines/script)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:14.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,672)}Yes, just emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:17.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You sure seem to be brimming with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.18,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1144,624)}No, I'm seriously not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:19.42,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(988,568)}I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tanaka is just great at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Can you just stop..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:24.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tanaka's already working seriously with Yomiuri TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:33.32,onscreen-white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(156,586)}Yomiuri TV
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:33.32,onscreen-white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(282,924)}Lead actor in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:33.32,onscreen-black,,0,0,0,,{\pos(287,1070.667)}"Settlement Lawyer"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:30.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,778)}The connection between \NTanaka and Yomiuri TV is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,1080.667)}He did an insane amount of work for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:38.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said, let's see Tanaka's acting skills as he takes on the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:40.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What scenario is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:47.02,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.42,Hamada panel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1246,333)}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:02:01.46,onscreen-white-big,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(276,842)\c&HB4B30D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\i1\fs60\fnMonotype Corsiva}Sad situation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:02:01.46,onscreen-white-big,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(1084,1015.667)}Visiting a grave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.70,Hamada panel,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0102F7&\pos(1244,333)}He's playing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:55.78,Endo Panel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1242,333)}Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:59.18,Hamada panel,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0102F7&\pos(1254,333)}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.46,Hosei Panel,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1242,333)\c&H0102F7&}Seriously, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:06.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Obviously, he can't hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:09.09,onscreen-black,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(756,925)\fs60\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H070600&}* Tanaka cannot hear the member's voices.*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So that we don't disrupt his concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:11.34,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Who's this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,His father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:16.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Maybe an ancestor? Depends on how Tanaka's looking at the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Looking at this face though,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:20.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,he's already begun acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,Sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's an actor after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:26.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He is an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.50,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's an actor's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It sure is, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:32.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like he's channeling it all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.70,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He looks like Saitou Yosuke here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's an actor, time to show his skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.32,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's been staring at it the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The acting's already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's slowly building up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.78,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He's doing well. Eyes are getting heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:46.78,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:48.38,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It's coming. It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.22,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.90,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's comin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:53.90,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's really coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yomiuri TV definitely won't be cutting him loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:02:59.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Fall, fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They won't let go of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Seriously, the tears won't fall if he blinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.62,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Wait until he cries, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:08.66,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Nope, he blinked once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.70,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He got excited instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And he was doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Just one more step and he'd have nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.74,Hosei,,0,0,0,,The thread of tension has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has let an early big chance go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to create that feeling once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But still, that's an actor's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.02,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.58,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He's attempting to pull it off from expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:45.74,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Rather than tricking the mind, he's trying to trick the brain with expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,His mouth though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.06,Hamada,,0,0,0,,it's shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:49.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,His mouth is shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's trying to trick his mind into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He sure is an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is where you've seriously just got to hang in there and keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.94,Endo,,0,0,0,,Once he crosses this hurdle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He couldn't pull it off on the previous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Come, come, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:04.34,Hamada,,0,0,0,,C'mon, c'mon, c'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:06.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,There, there, it's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When it's about to come out, he blinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.74,Endo,,0,0,0,,His heart is betraying him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's because he's making the expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,This pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:17.74,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:18.74,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(706,906)}It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:19.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm already tired of watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:26.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Certainly, nothing's really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Entering an unexpectedly long battle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The more he panics, the more he is unable to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.64,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No need to move your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.38,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That mouth is... cheap, isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A cheap move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Normally at those times there's a priest with a harisen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:53.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000007&\i0\fs42\pos(970,178)}Note: A harisen is a giant paper fan used for slapping. It is used to smack a funny man in response to their jokes or idiocy.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There has been no change whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.22,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's his normal face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's his normal face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's that normal face since his debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:03.66,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:07.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Only the time heartlessly passes by.
