Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, he widened his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:50.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's a public drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's looking up and having it open the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He might be able to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.16,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's really at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.74,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Using the glare of the studio lighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.30,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,901)}How cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's gonna burn his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Shameful and hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:15.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What's with the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:25.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000007&\i0\fs42\pos(810,224)}Note: Mori Shinichi is a Japanese male \Nenka singer and composer, who also \Nsings folk and pop music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like I said, Mori Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.74,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is Mori Shinichi when caring about his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:27.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"Eh? Really?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"Then, what song should I sing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:36.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,20 minutes pass
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Cocorico has seriously taken a boatload of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:46.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Really, how much time he's taking? More than all of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:47.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Cry already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:49.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the? This is new.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:54.22,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Compared to the previous expressions, this is something new. Isn't this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:57.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's should really just stop widening his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That was no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:05.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What impeccable timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:12.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Struggling with this hard time, but the conclusion wasn't long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.06,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.34,Hamada,,0,0,0,,The chance was at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.94,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's the way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Return faster man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You stink at acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:30.82,Endo,,0,0,0,,I stink at acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When you widened your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,I stink at acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:36.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking about when you were looking at the mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe I should take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:40.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Getting into Shikoku's mindset?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,That I got the championship belt mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You also looked at the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:46.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,The fight with Escargoman
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:48.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If you were thinking of such a thing, of course you weren't able to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What's the point of the fight anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end, only two members cleared and three failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:22:00.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For Tanaka who had worked on many dramas, hopefully this won't affect future offers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:02.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, wanna give it another go?
