Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:08.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:10.70,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.24,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,it's too difficult with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.34,Endo,,0,0,0,,This thing here is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:17.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,After using this return to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:19.68,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,906)}I'm going to borrow this.
